data.description: Cozy ranch home on .49 acre wooded lot only minutes from downtown Clayton. This 3bd/2bath home offers an Open Updated Kitchen accented w/ granite countertops, wet bar and ss appliances. Primary bath includes jacuzzi tub, tiled shower and tiled floor. Enjoy an evening relaxing in the large family room with eye catching floor to ceiling brick fireplace, or sitting out back on the newly installed Trex patio. Landscaped and private back yard with salt water private pool (needs new liner). Roof and gutters installed in 2021. Water heater new in 2020. HVAC replaced 7 years ago.
